課程概述 Course Description
       閱讀醫學類文章，學習基本的醫學知識、護理和保健。 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
In this course, you'll read articles written in the style of narrative medicine. You will learn basic knowledge in medicine, nursing, and health care. extbook developed by the NCKU Eagle Project will be used. The three foci in the textbook are:1. Illness symptoms and diagnosis2. Illness control and treatment3. Health education and promotion 

